title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
INDIANAPOLIS (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Indiana Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
07-10-13-30-44
(seven, ten, thirteen, thirty, forty-four)
Estimated jackpot: $90,000
